dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents land use for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2010. [This file folder contains the land use information for Fond du Lac County.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[The data are created to serve as base information for use in GIS systems for a variety of planning and analysis purposes. Use of data for Engineering work is prohibited.]
